  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.11">
<l>mātavaṉ pālcaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>tītava miṉṟi yuraitta</l>
<l>vētami lāyirat tippat</l>
<l>tōtaval lārpiṟa vārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are able to recite</l>
<l>these ten in the imperishable thousand</l>
<l>spoken without fiery penance</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ on Mādava</l>
	<l>will not be reborn.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
